/-- Line-Height: Referring to page No. 106 - from bible

use always 1 for large fonts(f6-f10), for short paragraphs 1.5 and 2 for long 
paragraphs --> â€” use a taller line-height for small text and a shorter 
line-height for large text.

Apart from below line-height values, no values will be accepted in design. Below
values are based on ratio of line-height

e.g. 
1. 12px font-size - line-height: 1 means - line height is 12px
2. 12px font-size - line-height: 1.5 means - line height is 18px etc.

-- string lh0: 1
-- string lh1: 1.5
-- string lh2: 1.75
-- string lh3: 2




